<B>__{view on michael}
<A>__{he has been listening to this discussion.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{pop, i've decided i'm going to enlist.}
<A>__{a quiet hush descends over the table, as though everyone knows the effect this will have on the old man. sonny tries to make light of it.}
